summary: This code snippet is used to terminate a Tmux session named "translator" and then load the configuration file "translator.yml" using Tmuxp, likely for testing purposes in the pyjom/tests/karaoke_effects folder.

details.comment: This code snippet is used to terminate a Tmux session named "translator" and then load the configuration file "translator.yml" using Tmuxp, likely for testing purposes in the pyjom/tests/karaoke_effects folder.
details.content:
tmux kill-session -t translator
tmuxp load -y translator.yml
